<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>InterviewIQ</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0f172a;
color:white;
min-height:100vh;
padding:30px;
}

.container{
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

h1{
font-size:55px;
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:10px;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#38bdf8,#8b5cf6);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.subtitle{
text-align:center;
color:#cbd5e1;
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.dashboard{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:25px;
}

.card{
background:#1e293b;
padding:25px;
border-radius:20px;
}

.card h2{
margin-bottom:20px;
}

input,textarea{
width:100%;
padding:14px;
margin-bottom:15px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
background:#334155;
color:white;
}

button{
width:100%;
padding:14px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
font-size:16px;
}

button:hover{
background:#1d4ed8;
}

.result{
margin-top:20px;
padding:15px;
background:#334155;
border-radius:12px;
display:none;
line-height:1.8;
}

.score{
font-size:60px;
text-align:center;
font-weight:bold;
color:#22c55e;
}

.progress{
height:12px;
background:#334155;
border-radius:10px;
margin-top:15px;
overflow:hidden;
}

.bar{
height:100%;
width:0%;
background:#22c55e;
transition:1s;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.dashboard{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

h1{
font-size:38px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>InterviewIQ</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
AI-Powered Interview Preparation Platform
</p>

<div class="dashboard">

<div class="card">

<h2>Candidate Profile</h2>

<input
type="text"
id="name"
placeholder="Your Name">

<input
type="text"
id="skills"
placeholder="Skills (HTML, CSS, JS...)">

<textarea
id="experience"
placeholder="Tell us about yourself">
</textarea>

<button onclick="analyzeProfile()">
Analyze Profile
</button>

<div class="result" id="questions"></div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Interview Readiness</h2>

<div class="score" id="score">
0%
</div>

<div class="progress">
<div class="bar" id="bar"></div>
</div>

<div class="result"
id="feedback"
style="display:block;">
Waiting for analysis...
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<script>

function analyzeProfile(){

let skills =
document.getElementById("skills").value;

if(skills===""){
alert("Enter skills");
return;
}

let score =
Math.floor(Math.random()*25)+75;

document.getElementById("score")
.innerText = score + "%";

document.getElementById("bar")
.style.width = score + "%";

document.getElementById("questions")
.style.display="block";

document.getElementById("feedback")
.style.display="block";

document.getElementById("questions")
.innerHTML =

`
<h3>Generated Interview Questions</h3>

<br>

1. Explain event delegation in JavaScript.

<br><br>

2. Difference between Flexbox and Grid?

<br><br>

3. What are Promises and Async/Await?

<br><br>

4. How would you optimize website performance?

<br><br>

5. Describe a project you are proud of.
`;

document.getElementById("feedback")
.innerHTML =

`
<b>AI Feedback</b>

<br><br>

✅ Strong technical profile

<br>

✅ Good skill diversity

<br>

⚠ Add more real-world projects

<br>

⚠ Improve system design understanding

<br><br>

Recommendation:
Practice mock interviews and build
one production-level project.
`;

}

</script>

</body>
</html>
